ProtoTheorem:
. "Suppose that $m,n\in\mathbf{N}$ and $\gcd(m,n)=1$. Then the
   map \begin{equation} \psi: (\Z/mn\Z{})^* \rightarrow 
   (\Z/m\Z{})^* \times (\Z/n\Z{})^*. \end{equation} defined by 
   $$ \psi(c) = (c mod m, \,\,c mod n) $$ is a bijection."
